(30288, 87346, 0, 3, 'Excuse Me', '', '2010-12-08 00:00:00', 2010, 0, 2, 1, '有人坐在我旁邊﹐一直看我看我的臉。\r\n我在想他的目的﹐是要問我幾個問題。\r\n其實我不會介意﹐只是想你可以換問題。\r\nEven before you open your mouth, I know what''s coming out\r\n \r\nExcuse me, where do you come from?How long you been here? Do you like Chinese food?\r\n你去過台灣的那裡﹖你一個人嗎 你會不會想你的家﹖\r\n \r\n有的人怕老外﹐我可以了解 cos so do I.\r\n可是他﹐他不會怕﹐他要跟我說話。\r\nI think I know what you''re gonna say, but that''s alright mate yeah that''s OK.\r\nWe''ll ignore other people''s stares, we''ll have a chat I don''t care.\r\n \r\nExcuse me, where do you come from?How long you been here? Do you like Chinese food?\r\n你去過台灣的那裡﹖你一個人嗎 你會不會想你的家﹖\r\n \r\nI think I''ve heard these before and it won''t be the last time I''m sure.\r\nBut it doesn''t bother me you can ask them again and again and again\r\n \r\nExcuse me, where do you come from?How long you been here? Do you like Chinese food?\r\n你去過台灣的那裡﹖你一個人嗎 你會不會想你的家﹖', '', 200, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2010-12-08 01:19:31', '2013-10-07 17:17:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
